       <span id="ctl00_pageContent_breadCrumbs"><a target="_self" href="/archives/home/" title="">Archives</a> &gt; <a target="_self" href="/Archives/Manuscripts/Manuscripts_Home/" title="">Manuscripts</a> &gt; <a target="_self" href="/Archives/Manuscripts/Faculty___Alumni_Papers/" title="Faculty &amp; Alumni Papers">Faculty &amp; Alumni Papers</a></span> 
